    <h2>April 1974</h2>
    <%= link_to image_tag("http://renaissancesoftware.net/paulgrenning/AprilPlaybackImage.jpg", :class => 'video', :id => "video_1"),
      'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UbYYwc5eDyA', :rel => "prettyPhoto[videos]", :title => "Playback of the year 1974"%>
    <p>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      The video below shows the year 1974. It is important for tornadoes because in 
      April of 1974 the most tornadoes touched down in a 2 day period ever recorded for a total of 147 tornadoes.
      The tornadoes killed 310 people, 5477 injuries, and at least 23 of them were rated F4 tornadoes.
      <br/>
      <br/>
      In the vidoe you will notice the small amounts of tornadoes in every month but April.
    </p>
  </div>
